Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you a story about my past?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About when I was in sixth grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once, a girl, one of my classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,brought a box of seven\Nor eight hamsters over by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They had bred after she'd been careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now she was at a loss,\Nunable to take care of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agreed to take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the way home, I filled up\Nan empty large fruit wine bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and drowned all of the hamsters in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours later, after dinner,\NI went to my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where I was captivated by what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One hamster, treading water\Nabove the other floating, lifeless hamsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it excited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I named the survivor Spice\Nand decided to raise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I saw it in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of the short story,\N"The Spider's Thread."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sinner named Kandata is in Hell\None day when Shakyamuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,moved by the single compassionate\Nact of his life, sparing a spider's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lowers a spider's thread\Ndown from Heaven to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kandata begins climbing\Ntowards Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kicking down at his fellow sinners\Nwhen they try to climb up after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the thread snaps,\Nand Kandata falls back down to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll believe this,\Nbut I'll tell you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I became acquainted with Spice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's as if I could see the spider's thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've murdered the people\Nwho I could see were connected to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point,\Na boy disrupted my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I saw a spider's thread
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,attached to the top of his head, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I named him Spice\Nand began observing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about you, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:43.25,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 987 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:01.23,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICHI REAL ESTATE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,\Ndidn't Satoru tell me once...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact is, you can go to Ueno\Nwithout changing trains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.31,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT, WONDER GUY!\NTV THEME SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:03.06,Sign Center,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FUNABASHI GENERAL HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe\Nyou were asleep for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fif... teen... years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll have to wait long\Nbefore starting rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom has spent four hours of every day\Nfor the last 15 years caring for my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the last three years,\Nshe's been using an EMS device{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to prepare for the day when I woke up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She took care of my joints\Nand my muscles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was 139 cm tall in fifth grade,\Nand now I'm 169 cm tall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Kitamura keeps saying,\N"This is all because of your mother"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and "It's remarkable."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Satoru, I think\Nthis is a good time for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the last thing you remember\Nbefore falling asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That memory was blocked,\Nlocked up tight behind a door.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face has changed a lot\Nsince you were 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories are scrambled too,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there may be discrepancies\Nregarding your sense of self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the time, I thought\Nmaybe he was right,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but even being in the Heisei era\Nfor the first time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}nothing felt out of place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.63,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PATIENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Patience." "Heart rate monitor."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.84,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEART RATE MONITOR
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.26,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SENSE OF LOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Sense of loss." "Arbitration."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.18,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ARBITRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can read all of these words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When in the world did I learn them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.77,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOYS' FLIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who am I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, you've got visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look good, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenya Kobayashi and Hiromi Sugita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were especially good friends of mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenya's a lawyer now,\Nand Hiromi's a doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I talked with them about trivial things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seemed that Kenya wanted\Nto ask me something,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I think Mom had given him\Nstrict instructions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we just chatted that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were a lot of things\NI wanted to ask them too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it seems Mom was trying\Nto avoid the topic of my past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom had been spending her life\Nfor the past 15 years only for me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}having faith\Nthat I would awaken one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's what Mom wishes,\NI guess I don't have to remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we call it a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.97,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11\NFuture
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kayo Sugita now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your baby's father is Hiromi then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like Hiromi wanted\Nto tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was about your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the baby has\NHiromi's long eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, even though he's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai... The "future"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\Nwe felt kind of uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "Is it all right\Nfor just us to become happy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we may have been\Nthe cause of you being in a coma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like we were leaving you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, my fate is my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you\Nto feel responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that what's become of me\Nwas a result of something I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were asleep for 15 years\Nbut still have a silver tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before, I could only imagine being alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but now I've got a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it was all made possible\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to spring all of this on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've tired you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Satoru. You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki was here a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I saw her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her baby's adorable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Photographers for gossip rags.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They want to write articles\Nabout you being in a coma for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to tell me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kitamura, when will I\Nbe able to walk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NThat could depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then from today, please let me\Ndo twice as much rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm anxious to walk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's making a smooth recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He could regain\Nhis memories at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I said the other day,\NI have to refuse that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My patient isn't a mouse—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:37.43,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SATORU FUJINUMA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your arms and legs\Nhave gotten a lot stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Mr. Fujinuma!\NYou really walked all that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was an awesome effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, Kenya is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to work with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We met several times\Nbefore you started elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was over 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He could never remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've waited 15 years for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be impatient now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got surgery\Nthe week after next, Kumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is going to\Ngive me her bone marrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that's what's going to cure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it true you were asleep for 15 years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here\Nfor about three months, huh, Kumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying all this time\Nto look good in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be really disappointed\Nonce you're out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tell you\Nhow to muster up courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You picture the smiling face\Nof someone who's dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you have to smile too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time's drifter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wakes up after 15 years,\Nis interested in little girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is a kid at heart with an adult's body,\Nand he may be released soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly taking photos\Nof a civilian in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Defamation, trespassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty to warrant punishment by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get your asses out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Nishizono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Fujinuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I was your\Nhomeroom teacher in fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gaku Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I go by "Nishizono" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my given name to "Manabu."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you change your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I got married five years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and was adopted into her\Nfamily as a son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father-in-law was a city council\Nmember for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but he passed away three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I inherited his constituency\Nand joined the council myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I changed\Nmy given name,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,keeping the kanji but going\Nwith the more common reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a politician now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still a freshman council member though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a feeling you'll make\Na great politician, Mr. Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met Kumi at a charity event\Nfor leukemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The director of this hospital is my\Nacquaintance, and he introduced us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found out you'd regained\Nconsciousness some time before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It took me long enough\Nto pay you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You went out of your way to visit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been anticipating\Nyour awakening for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't regained\Nall of your memories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remembering them gradually is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also going to see Kumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Her surgery is scheduled\Nfor the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this is the last day\Nshe can have visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I just saw her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, she was sleeping,\Nso I couldn't talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll try again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here,\Ndo you have time to chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I don't want to be interrupted\Nby the gossip mag hounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't we go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the perfect place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DELIVERIES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know\Nabout this elevator, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of an adventure, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you push the roof button?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it'd been a clear day,\Nthe sunset would've been beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there won't be any weird\Nphotographers up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The roof is really off limits,\Nso don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reminded of how you,\NKenya and Hiromi often said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go to the hideout!"\NYour pretend secret base, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my memories back!
